        {
            "order": 1,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "I feel sick. My head hurts.",
            "translation": "حالم بد است. سرم درد می‌کند."
        },
        {
            "order": 2,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Do you have a fever?",
            "translation": "تب دارید؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 3,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Yes, since yesterday.",
            "translation": "بله، از دیروز دارم."
        },
        {
            "order": 4,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Does your throat hurt too?",
            "translation": "گلویتان هم درد می‌کند؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 5,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "A little. And I feel very tired.",
            "translation": "کمی. و خیلی خسته‌ام."
        },
        {
            "order": 6,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "It sounds like you have a cold.",
            "translation": "به نظر می‌رسد سرما خورده‌اید."
        },
        {
            "order": 7,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "What should I do?",
            "translation": "چه کار باید بکنم؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 8,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Drink a lot of water and get some rest.",
            "translation": "آب زیاد بنوشید و کمی استراحت کنید."
        },
        {
            "order": 9,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Take this medicine two times a day.",
            "translation": "این دارو را روزی دو بار مصرف کنید."
        },
        {
            "order": 10,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "How many days?",
            "translation": "چند روز؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 11,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "For five days. You will feel better soon.",
            "translation": "پنج روز. به‌زودی بهتر می‌شوید."
        },
        {
            "order": 12,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Thank you, doctor.",
            "translation": "ممنون، دکتر."
        },
        {
            "order": 13,
